&lt;p id="JqxlkC"&gt;A &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/29/24309116/lenovo-accidentally-confirms-legion-go-s-yet-again-with-a-budget-amd-chip"&gt;firmware leak last week&lt;/a&gt; for the “Legion Go S 8ARP1” indicated the cheaper machine will have AMD’s Rembrandt APU inside. &lt;/p&gt;
