&lt;p id="jTU8fl"&gt;While it’s based on a new Ryzen Z2 platform, &lt;a href="https://videocardz.com/newz/lenovo-confirms-legion-go-s-gaming-handheld-with-amd-rembrandt-apu-via-firmware-leak"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Videocardz&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; points out the chip will have Zen 3-plus cores that aren’t as powerful as the current generation Z1 Extreme with Zen 4 cores inside the current Legion Go.&lt;/p&gt;
