      &lt;img alt="GM logo illustration" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R4D-fgmpffUvW9i-My_J3ayOSYg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762223/acastro_STK057_01.0.jpg" /&gt;
