      &lt;img alt="Photo illustration of Elon Musk surrounded by raining dollar bills." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SJcp2Vr8h_M0gj1pgCCWePxRzeg=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73762188/STK022_ELON_MUSK_CVIRGINIA_E.0.jpg" /&gt;
